data.description:
Hard to find home on 2.5 acres in Durant School District. The 3 bedroom 2 bath floor plan features a split bedroom design with an open concept Living room and kitchen. This manufactured home includes a large front porch, carport, Shop, Storm Cellar, A Large yard, and much more. Home was updated in 2017. Sellers will pay $2,500 of buyer’s closing cost.  
Broker is related to Sellers.
